    "long_instructions": "#### Predict\r\n\r\nThis program has some new blocks! Before we run our code, let's write down some thoughts on what we think might happen.\r\n\r\n1) Write down anything you **notice** about the code. _It's okay to write things that feel obvious, like \"the new block is a different color\"_\r\n2) Make a **prediction** - what do you think will happen when you press Run? _This is just a guess - it's okay to be unsure!_\r\n\r\nOnce you've answered the questions, Press \"Run\" and listen. Then wait for next steps from your teacher.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
